qDef.qDef:
Pick
    (
        [%SynHeadersExpectedYearClosingAnalysis]
        ,Sum({$<[Sales Type] = {'Net Sales'}, [Month ID] =  , Year = {$(v_Max_Year_LY)} , Quarter=, Month=, [Month Year]=>} [Invoice MT])
        
        ,	(Sum({$<[Sales Type] = {'Forecast'}, [Month ID] =  , Year = {$(v_Max_Year)} , Quarter=, Month=, [Month Year]=>} [EYC Kg - Forecast] ) 
        	+ Sum({$<[Sales Type] = {'Net Sales'}, [Month ID] =  , Year = {$(v_Max_Year)} , Quarter=, Month=, [Month Year]=>} [EYC Kg - Invoiced] ))/1000
        
        ,Sum({$<[Sales Type] = {'Budget'}, [Month ID] =  , Year = {$(v_Max_Year)} , Quarter=, Month=, [Month Year]=>} [Budget MT])
        
         ,Sum({$<[Sales Type] = {'Budget'}, [Month ID] =  , Year = {$(v_Max_Year_Plus1)} , Quarter=, Month=, [Month Year]=>} [Budget MT])
         
          , (Sum({$<[Sales Type] = {'Forecast'}, [Month ID] =  , Year = {$(v_Max_Year)} , Quarter=, Month=, [Month Year]=>} [EYC Kg - Forecast] ) 
        	+ Sum({$<[Sales Type] = {'Net Sales'}, [Month ID] =  , Year = {$(v_Max_Year)} , Quarter=, Month=, [Month Year]=>} [EYC Kg - Invoiced] ))/1000
            
            -Sum({$<[Sales Type] = {'Budget'}, [Month ID] =  , Year = {$(v_Max_Year)} , Quarter=, Month=, [Month Year]=>} [Budget MT]) 
        , (Sum({$<[Sales Type] = {'Forecast'}, [Month ID] =  , Year = {$(v_Max_Year)} , Quarter=, Month=, [Month Year]=>} [EYC Kg - Forecast] ) 
        	+ Sum({$<[Sales Type] = {'Net Sales'}, [Month ID] =  , Year = {$(v_Max_Year)} , Quarter=, Month=, [Month Year]=>} [EYC Kg - Invoiced] ))/1000
            
            -Sum({$<[Sales Type] = {'Net Sales'}, [Month ID] =  , Year = {$(v_Max_Year_LY)} , Quarter=, Month=, [Month Year]=>} [Invoice MT])
         
    )

Pick
    (
        [%SynHeadersExpectedYearClosingAnalysis]
        ,Sum({$<[Sales Type] = {'Net Sales'}, [Month ID] =  , Year = {$(v_Max_Year_LY)} ,[Currency Sorting Key]={$(=MaxString([Currency Sorting Key]))}, Quarter=, Month=, [Month Year]=>} [Invoice Amount USD]*[Currency Average Rate])
        
        ,	(Sum({$<[Sales Type] = {'Forecast'}, [Month ID] =  , Year = {$(v_Max_Year)} ,[Currency Sorting Key]={$(=MaxString([Currency Sorting Key]))}, Quarter=, Month=, [Month Year]=>} [EYC Amount USD - Forecast]*[Currency Average Rate] ) 
        	+ Sum({$<[Sales Type] = {'Net Sales'}, [Month ID] =  , Year = {$(v_Max_Year)} ,[Currency Sorting Key]={$(=MaxString([Currency Sorting Key]))}, Quarter=, Month=, [Month Year]=>} [EYC Amount USD - Invoiced]*[Currency Average Rate] ))
        
        ,Sum({$<[Sales Type] = {'Budget'}, [Month ID] =  , Year = {$(v_Max_Year)} , Quarter=,[Currency Sorting Key]={$(=MaxString([Currency Sorting Key]))}, Month=, [Month Year]=>} [Budget Amount USD]*[Currency Average Rate])
        
         ,Sum({$<[Sales Type] = {'Budget'}, [Month ID] =  , Year = {$(v_Max_Year_Plus1)} ,[Currency Sorting Key]={$(=MaxString([Currency Sorting Key]))}, Quarter=, Month=, [Month Year]=>} [Budget Amount USD]*[Currency Average Rate])
         
          , (Sum({$<[Sales Type] = {'Forecast'}, [Month ID] =  , Year = {$(v_Max_Year)} ,[Currency Sorting Key]={$(=MaxString([Currency Sorting Key]))}, Quarter=, Month=, [Month Year]=>} [EYC Amount USD - Forecast]*[Currency Average Rate] ) 
        	+ Sum({$<[Sales Type] = {'Net Sales'}, [Month ID] =  , Year = {$(v_Max_Year)} ,[Currency Sorting Key]={$(=MaxString([Currency Sorting Key]))}, Quarter=, Month=, [Month Year]=>} [EYC Amount USD - Invoiced]*[Currency Average Rate]  ))
            
            -Sum({$<[Sales Type] = {'Budget'}, [Month ID] =  , Year = {$(v_Max_Year)} ,[Currency Sorting Key]={$(=MaxString([Currency Sorting Key]))}, Quarter=, Month=, [Month Year]=>} [Budget Amount USD]*[Currency Average Rate]) 
        , (Sum({$<[Sales Type] = {'Forecast'}, [Month ID] =  , Year = {$(v_Max_Year)} ,[Currency Sorting Key]={$(=MaxString([Currency Sorting Key]))}, Quarter=, Month=, [Month Year]=>} [EYC Amount USD - Forecast]*[Currency Average Rate]  ) 
        	+ Sum({$<[Sales Type] = {'Net Sales'}, [Month ID] =  , Year = {$(v_Max_Year)} ,[Currency Sorting Key]={$(=MaxString([Currency Sorting Key]))}, Quarter=, Month=, [Month Year]=>} [EYC Amount USD - Invoiced]*[Currency Average Rate]  ))
            
            -Sum({$<[Sales Type] = {'Net Sales'}, [Month ID] =  , Year = {$(v_Max_Year_LY)} ,[Currency Sorting Key]={$(=MaxString([Currency Sorting Key]))}, Quarter=, Month=, [Month Year]=>} [Invoice Amount USD]*[Currency Average Rate])
         
    )  /1000
